      "message": "Today each referenced board (GPU or switch) exposes exactly one NvidiaMctpVdm config, so dbus-sensors resolves it unambiguously by board name and a plain-string Board is sufficient. If a board ever needs multiple NvidiaMctpVdm configs, we\u0027ll switch Board (and BridgedEndpoints) to an {Entity, Name} object and update dbus-sensors to select the config by Name instead of taking the first match.",
